        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"synaxim-symbiotic-gate-fine-tuning\">\ud83e\uddec SYNAXIM \u2014 Symbiotic Gate Fine-Tuning</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Goal</strong>: Fine-tune Llama 3.2 1B so it produces coherent text through the Symbiotic Gate.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Method</strong>: Knowledge distillation \u2014 use the standard attention outputs as teacher, \ntrain the model to produce similar outputs through the O(1) M-matrix gate.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Steps</strong>:</span>\n<ol>\n<li>Load Llama 3.2 1B (standard PyTorch)</li>\n<li>Generate teacher hidden states with standard attention</li>\n<li>Train a gate adapter to make Symbiotic Gate match teacher</li>\n<li>Export adapted weights to <code>.symb</code> format</li>\n<li>Push to HuggingFace</li>\n</ol></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
